data.description: This is one you have to see to believe!!  Here you have an amazing home that is move in ready and everything is updated and ready to go for you.....   As soon as you walk in you will fall in love with everything this home has to offer you and everyone else you might bring with you for the move in.  There is an amazing four season room in the front of the house that leads into the perfect entertainment area.  The 1st floor has an open concept with a HUGE living room and an absolutely stunning kitchen.  There is an even a powder room on the 1st floor.  The kitchen in this home is absolutely amazing!   The size, counter space and the fact that it is an eat in kitchen is something that you will have a hard time finding any where else.  Also the kitchen has a great mud room in the back that is the perfect space for the washer and dryer.  From the mud room you can walk out to the back yard that is perfect for grilling in the summer time.  Add in the fact that there are stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, amazing cabinetry and beautiful ceramic gray tile floors make this one of a kind kitchen.  As you go upstairs you will find 3 great sized bedrooms and full bathroom.  Not only that but one of the bedrooms actually has a balcony attached on the 2nd floor.   With the neutral colors throughout the home and the beautiful finishes the only thing this house is missing is YOU!  All you have to do is move in your furniture and make yourself at home...
